&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4506&quot; title=&quot;[hbck] Allow HBaseFsck to be instantiated without connecting&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4506&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4506&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
